products.title: Essence Tango Venetian Blind - 25mm Slat
products.description: Orange is an in colour and its easy to see why when you look at this essence tango blind. Perhaps a tad bold to be used in an all orange scheme, it makes the perfect accent to lighter hues. Used in a bedroom, its guaranteed to get the juices flowing from the moment you wake orange is an in colour and its easy to see why when you look at this essence tango blind.
